    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was liberated in 1945, too, with-- with a few girlfriends-- what they all live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I went to [? visit ?] Israel four years ago, I met them.",
